@endgroup

@group traffic-distribution-group
@endpoint DELETE /traffic-distribution-group/{TrafficDistributionGroupId}
@desc Deletes a traffic distribution group. This API can be called only in the Region where the traffic distribution group is created. For more information about deleting traffic distribution groups, see Delete traffic distribution groups in the Amazon Connect Administrator Guide.
